<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title>UVCI e-Reclamations | Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f3f3;
            font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        h1 {
            background-color: #430243;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 0 50px 0;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 3px solid #264459;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fefefe;
            width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .bottom {
            background-color: #efefee;
        }

        .block {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 20px 20px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #430243;
            color: #fefefe;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-green {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #04691d;
            color: #fefefe;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header text-center">
                <a href="{{ url('account') }}">
                    <img src="https://campus.uvci.edu.ci/mooc/assets/images/logouvci2.png" class="logo" alt="Logo UVCI">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h1 class="text-center">Nouvelle Réclamation</h1>
                <p class="block">
                    Bonjour,<br>
                    Une réclamation portant sur le<strong> {{ evaluation_wording }} / {{ evaluation_matter }} / {{evaluation_semester}} </strong>vient d'être postée sur la plateforme des réclamations.
                </p>
                <p class="block">
                    <span class="btn">Détails de la Réclamation</span>
                </p>
                <p class="block">
                    <strong>Objet : {{ claim_wording }}</strong><br>
                    <strong>Desc. :</strong><br>{{ claim_content }}
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p class="block text-center">
                    <a href="{{ url('account') }}" class="btn-green">Se Connecter</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>